Classic 2048 gameplay on a configurable 4x4 grid.
Java backend managing game state, moves, merges, and score.
Angular frontend dynamically displays the game board and score.
Full state synchronization via REST calls.
Keyboard controls for moving tiles (Arrow keys).
Game restart from the UI.
Game over detection with alerts.

Layer          |  Technology            
---------------+------------------------
Backend        |  Java 17, Spring Boot 3
Frontend       |  Angular 17, TypeScript
Communication  |  REST APIs using HTTP  

mvn clean install
mvn spring-boot:run


Front End 
npm install
ng serve


Open browser at http://localhost:4200/.
